      • of

        public static BuildInfo of(Class referenceClass)
        Returns build info for diversicon maven packages. In order for this to work there must be file BUILD_PROPERTIES_PATH in specified class resources. If not present, logs an error and returns an empty object.
        Since:
        0.1.0
        See Also:
        hasProperties(Class)
